propSpec.name: calculationEntries
propSpec.desc: A list containing each entry inside the calculation string and it's associated data

propSpec.name: selectEntryIndex
propSpec.desc: A number which sets any given entry by its index. This happens by default when selecting an entry but can be set programmatically to select an entry

propSpec.name: splitCalculationStringBy
propSpec.desc: The characters by which are used to split the calculation string when it has been modified

propSpec.name: ignoreWordsList
propSpec.desc: A list of words which should cannot be split by the splitCalculationStringBy flag
